					<h3 class="text-slate-900 text-sm md:text-md mb-1 text-base" itemprop="name">{{ 'Goal 16: Promote peaceful and inclusive societies for sustainable development, provide access to justice for all and build effective, accountable and inclusive institutions at all levels'|t }}</h3>
